markets.title: End Of Summer streams by Aug 1, 2025?
markets.rules_primary: If End Of Summer  by Tame Impala  has above 7 million total streams on Spotify by Aug 1, 2025 at 10 AM ET, then the market resolves to Yes.
markets.rules_secondary: Total stream count will be determined using the Spotify desktop app at 10 AM ET, based on the exact number displayed at that time. Any updates or changes after 10 AM ET will NOT be considered. The following song can be found here: https://open.spotify.com/track/1Iw5iLfAwDvS6frI82gMoV?si=c4d17faed4134aa8
markets.early_close_condition: This market will close and expire early if the event occurs.
